                <div class="glossary-related">
                  <h4 class="glossary-section-title">üìö Èñ¢ÈÄ£„Ç≥„É≥„ÉÜ„É≥„ÉÑ <span class="glossary-related-count">({relatedVideos.length + relatedArticles.length + relatedNotes.length}‰ª∂)</span></h4>
                  <div class="glossary-related-articles">
                    {relatedVideos.map(video => (
                      <div class="glossary-related-item">
